Gombe State Governor,  Alhaji Muhammadu Inuwa Yahaya, has felicitated with his Kaduna State counterpart, Malam Nasir Ahmad el-Rufa’i as he turns 60 today. In a goodwill message he personally signed and released by his Senior Special Assistant on Media and Publicity, Ismaila Uba Misilli, Inuwa Yahaya commended the tenacity and unwavering commitment of Malam el-Rufa’i in the execution of developmental projects and programmes in his state. He noted that “Your pedigree of excellence,  tenacity,  courage and remarkable performance have stood you out and made you a reference point of good governance and positive transformation.” Hajj 2020: Kaduna to begin public enlightenment Virus spreads on ship in Japan, American passengers set to… Oshiomhole donates 200 bags of rice to IDPs in Taraba NPDC emerges best exploration, production company in 2019 ALSO READ: Oshiomhole donates 200 bags of rice to IDPs in Taraba The governor further stated that “I join the good people of Kaduna State and indeed millions of your well-wishers in celebrating your attainment of three scores which is a great milestone in life worthy of celebration.” He lauded the governor for using his good office to impact positively on the lives of many and well as for his strive to restore the lost glory of Kaduna State. The Gombe governor then prayed to Almighty Allah to continue to bless Governor el-Rufa’i with good health, wisdom and long life to keep serving the fatherland and humanity. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE.